snippet.title: Waking Nitemare: Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
We are excited to announce that the Early Access for Waking Nitemare, the game we have been working hard on, will be starting soon.

By the way, the game's name has dramatically changed from Waking Nightmare to Waking Nitemare!
